originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.p_name,
    s.s_name,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_quantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders,
    AVG(o.o_totalprice) AS avg_order_price,
    CONCAT(r.r_name, ' - ', n.n_name) AS region_nation
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON o.o_custkey = s.s_nationkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    p.p_comment LIKE 'Special%' 
    AND o.o_orderdate BETWEEN '1996-01-01' AND '1996-12-31'
    AND s.s_acctbal > 500.00
GROUP BY 
    p.p_name, s.s_name, r.r_name, n.n_name
HAVING 
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) > 1000
ORDER BY 
    avg_order_price DESC, total_orders DESC
FETCH FIRST 10 ROWS ONLY

INNER JOIN (SELECT "t1"."p_partkey", "t1"."p_name", "t1"."p_mfgr", "t1"."p_brand", "t1"."p_type", "t1"."p_size", "t1"."p_container", "t1"."p_retailprice", "t1"."p_comment", "t1"."ps_partkey", "t1"."ps_suppkey", "t1"."ps_availqty", "t1"."ps_supplycost", "t1"."ps_comment", "t1"."s_suppkey", "t1"."s_name", "t1"."s_address", "t1"."s_nationkey", "t1"."s_phone", "t1"."s_acctbal", "t1"."s_comment", "t2"."o_orderkey", "t2"."o_custkey", "t2"."o_orderstatus", "t2"."o_totalprice", "t2"."o_orderdate", "t2"."o_orderpriority", "t2"."o_clerk", "t2"."o_shippriority", "t2"."o_comment"
FROM (SELECT "part"."p_partkey", "part"."p_name", "part"."p_mfgr", "part"."p_brand", "part"."p_type", "part"."p_size", "part"."p_container", "part"."p_retailprice", "part"."p_comment", "s1"."ps_partkey", "s1"."ps_suppkey", "s1"."ps_availqty", "s1"."ps_supplycost", "s1"."ps_comment", "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name", "supplier"."s_address", "supplier"."s_nationkey", "supplier"."s_phone", "supplier"."s_acctbal", "supplier"."s_comment", CAST("supplier"."s_nationkey" AS BIGINT) AS "s_nationkey0"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "s1"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey"
WHERE "part"."p_comment" LIKE 'Special%' AND "supplier"."s_acctbal" > 500.00) AS "t1"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "orders"
WHERE "o_orderdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "o_orderdate" <= DATE '1996-12-31') AS "t2" ON "t1"."s_nationkey0" = "t2"."o_custkey") AS "t3" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "t3"."s_nationkey"
GROUP BY "t3"."p_name", "t3"."s_name", "region"."r_name", "nation"."n_name"
HAVING SUM("t3"."ps_availqty") > 1000
ORDER BY 7 DESC NULLS FIRST, 6 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t7"

FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
WHERE "part"."p_comment" LIKE 'Special%' AND "supplier"."s_acctbal" > 500.00) AS "t1"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "s1"
WHERE "o_orderdate" >= DATE '1996-01-01' AND "o_orderdate" <= DATE '1996-12-31') AS "t2" ON "t1"."s_nationkey0" = "t2"."o_custkey") AS "t3" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "t3"."s_nationkey"
GROUP BY "t3"."p_name", "t3"."s_name", "region"."r_name", "nation"."n_name"
HAVING SUM("t3"."ps_availqty") > 1000
ORDER BY 7 DESC NULLS FIRST, 6 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t7"
